{"tid":1553013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港恐怖份子對市民 遊客 記者 射出多次催淚毒氣","createTime":"2019-09-08T12:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T12:28:34.000Z","uid":47905,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c4cec71ed1efee2b987156590f9150d0e1702f4c","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T12:59:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/679683935832505/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F679683935832505%2F&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=e49d74f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/679683935832505/</a><br />\n<br />\n有外藉人士倒地<br />\n有市民需要洗眼<br />\n<br />\n呢單一定要推上國際<br />\n<br />\n香港恐怖份子想殺市民 遊客 記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n清楚睇到條街係無示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁都唔推上國際?<br />\n<br />\n仲有,呢班唔係黑警,唔係黑社會<br />\n係香港武裝恐怖份子<br />\n只有恐怖份子先會對市民 遊客 做出呢D野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以唔該 以後正名<br />\n香港恐怖份子/香港武裝恐怖份子"},{"pid":"d8ea0e3cae92963be6e74a6e0527938a346a3114","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1d57bb429d7db9c87a5144886f6f25fd2f14553","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:01:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZtjNbj3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZtjNbj3.jpg&h=8b898ea5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇一睇呢班恐怖份子既傑作"},{"pid":"c46f9f2ec52a05f910700fd613cac7dcc92045ec","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:03:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyNY_WpzV1k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DQyNY_WpzV1k&d=h%2B0F1AfFk4MBaO73S6qK%2BtVSC25YwgVwXuaRRXYDXIw%3D&h=5e8bfebe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QyNY_WpzV1k</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/VJ2Z2XT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVJ2Z2XT.gif&h=d6808803&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"92753563650802107c868824ddbdb57b1e466217","tid":1553013,"uid":203813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:03:27.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"7e502e72d9a918e8675051f5c5543665aef9551b","tid":1553013,"uid":2126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:04:15.000Z","msg":"有個鬼佬訓低左"},{"pid":"cc74cce602e739956d41f92c967bef85b72f8ead","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:04:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/G1DRMA2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FG1DRMA2.jpg&h=79c35124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n恐怖份子先會當街非禮"},{"pid":"637390c70cf280c6bfc38685706d142bb1aa792d","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:05:06.000Z","msg":"蘋果又有講<br />\n男警搜女仔身"},{"pid":"c09e4175e14129b1f437496529995615a5a6275f","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T13:06:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1c840c02606dedec69668c3b0652bc292e437c","tid":1553013,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T1